Elsa Pataky https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elsa_Pataky 0 Elsa Lafuente Medianu (born 18 July 1976), known professionally as Elsa Pataky, is a Spanish model, actress, and film producer. Pataky is known for her role as Elena Neves in The Fast and the Furious franchise. She has appeared in the films Snakes on a Plane (2006), Giallo (2009) and Give 'Em Hell, Malone (2009). She also starred in the Spanish film Di Di Hollywood in 2010. Elsa_Lafuente_Medianu ( born 18_July_1976 ) , known professionally as Elsa_Pataky , is a_Spanish_model , actress , and film_producer .
